## Drizzle
Use drizzle **only for migrations**, **not for queries**.

## Syntax
Use the following syntax:

For SQLite, use the following syntax:
```sql
import { sqlite } from "@/lib/sqlite";

const data = {
  title: "Hello World",
  content: "This is a test post",
};
return sqlite`INSERT INTO posts ${sqlite(data)} RETURNING *`;
```

For Postgres, use the following syntax:
```sql
import { sql } from "bun";

const data = {
  title: "Hello World",
  content: "This is a test post",
};
return sql`INSERT INTO posts ${sql(data)} RETURNING *`;
```